### ===============================================
### SUMMARY - Expected Results
### ===============================================

# HELP_DESK CAN DO (Should return 200/201 OK):
# ✅ View all incidents
# ✅ Create incidents (PRIMARY!)
# ✅ Update incidents
# ✅ Assign incidents
# ✅ Reassign incidents
# ✅ Close incidents (PRIMARY! with photo)
# ✅ Cancel incidents
# ✅ Delete incidents
# ✅ CRUD Stores (all operations)
# ✅ CRUD Equipment (all operations)
# ✅ View statistics (all data)

# HELP_DESK CANNOT DO (Should return 403 Forbidden):
# ❌ Accept incidents (TECHNICIAN only)
# ❌ Resolve incidents (TECHNICIAN only)

